HEADWORD: Xanthoproteic
<hw>Xan`tho*pro*te"ic</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <fld>(Physiol.
Chem.)</fld> <def>Pertaining to, or derived from, xanthoprotein; showing
